{"tid":1019490,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜為夢想晚2年高中畢業！　全力衝事業「放棄大學生活」","createTime":"2019-02-13T03:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T09:05:09.000Z","uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"263ed6cfab75c7ec6f67161583b6ef596ae2457c","tid":1019490,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"子瑜為夢想晚2年高中畢業！　全力衝事業「放棄大學生活」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PVELLfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPVELLfw.jpg&h=a2225ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲TWICE成員子瑜決定不升學，全力衝刺事業。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n子瑜國二時前往南韓開始練習生，同時也轉學至位於首爾的「韓國漢城華僑中學」繼續學業。為了繼續升學，子瑜2016年曾返台參加國中同等學力鑑定考試，拿到台灣的國中學歷後，再隔一年才正式成為「高中生」，錄取翰林藝術高中實用音樂科。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3890/d3890703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3890%2Fd3890703.jpg&h=d1d3120b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE子瑜高中畢業照。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n今年20歲的子瑜為了出道夢想，輾轉多花了2年才從高中畢業，如今看來也是值得。而身為現今最當紅KPOP女團成員，子瑜去年11月就沒有參加南韓的大學修業能力考試（大學入學測驗），據韓媒報導，未來將集中在演藝活動上，放棄在入學當大學生新鮮人的機會。"},{"pid":"33a0b677848a565b4b2a57457fc9483f678da25b","tid":1019490,"uid":80814,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"以佢嘅行程, 有得攞埋高中學歷算好,<br />\n好多未成年就出道嘅idol, <br />\n未讀完高中就輟學, 好多得初中學歷<br />\n同埋韓國人最重視高考,<br />\nidol參加高考或者入大學係會被人鬧阻住啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca32ebf92dc751a6c31230d49a84929e9eb13fa","tid":1019490,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:56:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 , 還我透明人"},{"pid":"b1dc6156e6e2da0464cd1304b85f1aa05cd9ac02","tid":1019490,"uid":815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"33a0b677848a565b4b2a57457fc9483f678da25b","tid":1019490,"uid":80814,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"以佢嘅行程, 有得攞埋高中學歷算好,<br />\n好多未成年就出道嘅idol, <br />\n未讀完高中就輟學, 好多得初中學歷<br />\n同埋韓國人最重視高考,<br />\nidol參加高考或者入大學係會被人鬧阻住啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"點會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國得幾間大學有用<br />\n啲idol有料入到有咩好屌"},{"pid":"70dc7e5469116e113f62eb97f00c0976a1c4f02d","tid":1019490,"uid":50658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:58:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢去大學我都願意為子瑜重返校園<br />\n<br />\n做佢組爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736e649739b87432bbf6a0cb8e7a2fd54492e611","tid":1019490,"uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73e90f616c80f0b75cf580685362a41ca30eaaa","tid":1019490,"uid":12019,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b1dc6156e6e2da0464cd1304b85f1aa05cd9ac02","tid":1019490,"uid":815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"33a0b677848a565b4b2a57457fc9483f678da25b","tid":1019490,"uid":80814,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"以佢嘅行程, 有得攞埋高中學歷算好,<br />\n好多未成年就出道嘅idol, <br />\n未讀完高中就輟學, 好多得初中學歷<br />\n同埋韓國人最重視高考,<br />\nidol參加高考或者入大學係會被人鬧阻住啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"點會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓國得幾間大學有用<br />\n啲idol有料入到有咩好屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"有幾多真係靠有料入去阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本就係黑箱作業 韓國最撚興"},{"pid":"7004531a8f73b65545019da6641ff865ea7ae3e4","tid":1019490,"uid":3112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b1dc6156e6e2da0464cd1304b85f1aa05cd9ac02","tid":1019490,"uid":815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"33a0b677848a565b4b2a57457fc9483f678da25b","tid":1019490,"uid":80814,"like":24,"